AudioFormat, ClassFormat, CsvFormat, DatFormat, FontFormat, GifFormat, GzipFormat, ImageFormat, JarFormat, JsonFormat, MidiFormat, PropertyFormat, TextFormat, XmlFormat, ZipFormat
public abstract class BaseAssetFormat
extends Object
implements AssetFormat

An abstract AssetFormat that requires the format's extensions and available output (request) types at creation time.

Author:
Philip Diffenderfer
